        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1413",
        "content": "First of all came the little episode from the time of my courting, of which I have already spoken; the pressure of a hand under the table gave rise in the dream to the \"under the table,\" which I had subsequently to find a place for in my recollection.",
