        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1413",
        "content": "Its mode of action thus consists in so cooerdinating the parts of the dream that these coalesce to a coherent whole, to a dream composition.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
